en Things in the Song of Ice and Fire books has always been one of the most compelling reasons, for me, to read and re-read these great books.<br /><br />The guys at HBO have also done a tremendous job showing this brilliantly in the show. Well done all around, and thanks for the continuing greatness of this series.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"October 23 2013, 16:58:56 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Fantastic!","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/chad.cottle","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Chad Cottle","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_423231","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=34690242&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Chad Cottle","ctime_ts":1382547536,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/122072242/67014662","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373434#t18373434","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373434#t18373434","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373434#t18373434","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_2233869","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/zahudica","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":18373434,"talkid":71771,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373434#t18373434","upictitle":"Zahudica: pic#122072242","article":"Dear mr Martin, although it is GOT which got the award, it's your books that really deserve it. No offense to HBO, D&D etc., but watching the show almost made me forget how brilliant your writing is. I mean, although it's a good show in its own right, it doesn't come close to ASOIAF. I'll stop blabbing now - in short, well done, ser! ;)","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"October 23 2013, 17:26:11 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/zahudica","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"zahudica","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2233869","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=67014662&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"zahudica","ctime_ts":1382549171,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/123609833/40283036","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373946#t18373946","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373946#t18373946","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373946#t18373946","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"hummelchen3","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://hummelchen3.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":18373946,"talkid":71773,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/342842.html?thread=18373946#t18373946","upictitle":"hummelchen3: pic#123609833","article":"This is really a meaningful award! And while I agree that the reasons for this kind of recognition is the series (David and Dan etc.) it was always your story and your characters. So you indeed can be proud of that!  I really liked that bit that Radcliffe wrote to you.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"October 23 2013, 18:32:53 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"usernam